{
  "stem": "26609.16",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I knew that-- I understood that must be a trick.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "But it is what she said.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "It was dark blood.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "I didn't think much, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] because if I would think, I would come to the same conclusion.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "They're going to kill me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "So I fainted and fell to the floor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "Till then, I never faint.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "My life, I never faint, fainted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "Once when I took my child after kilometers walking to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And second time, I fell.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "When I woke up, I was in another room on those field beds.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And she said-- [PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] I came to myself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And she said, Wanda, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "That's why I can't forgive myself is that I didn't do it till now.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "We are going home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "Everything will be all right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "She didn't say, you are Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "She didn't say anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "She just said, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "We are going home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And everything will be all right.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "She settled it with him, I found out later, for hundreds and hundreds or maybe more Deutsche Mark and products from the farm-- chickens and cheese and milk and meat, whatever.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] Went out, never a word, nothing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "It went on as it was before.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "She had a friend who was assigned, I think, by the government, because all men were in the field, in the war.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "But those men who had farms and paid a lot to the government were staying home.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "But they were assigned to help others, women, whose husbands' farms-- whose husbands were in the war, and the women couldn't carry on the whole farm.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "Hers was one of the largest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "She was very wealthy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "So he was assigned to help her out.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
